General.Name: Jupiter Gold Corporation
General.Description: Jupiter Gold Corporation engages in the exploration and development of gold and other metal mining properties in Brazil. The company also explores for palladium, platinum, quartzite, and manganese ores. It holds 100% interest in various gold projects, which are in development and exploratory stages totaling 154,000 acres, and an active mineral right for quartzite and manganese with 233 acres. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is based in Olhos-d`Água, Brazil.
